T1  - An Approach for Assessing and Managing Inter-Unit Interdependence
AU  - McCann, Joseph E.
AU  - Ferry, Diane L.
Y1  - 1979/01/01
PY  - 1979
DA  - 1979/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1979.4289199
